opam-version: "2.0"
synopsis: "A static site generator"
description: """
Camyll is a static site generator.

Features:

- Conversion from Markdown to HTML
- Syntax highlighting of any language via user-provided TextMate grammars
- Post tagging
- Processing of literate Agda"""
